com.nokia.maps.search

Interface GeocodeRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SearchRequest
    Deprecated. 
    use GeocodeRequest

    public interface GeocodeRequest
extends SearchRequest
    This interface defines a request which is used to search for geographical locations. A single GeoCode request may multiple Locations for a single search.
